---
import { icon } from '../lib/icons';
import { WHATSAPP_URL, waUrl, REGISTER_URL } from '../lib/site';
---

<section id="contato" class="relative py-28 sm:py-36">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="reveal beam relative overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-suede-500/25 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800/80 via-navy-900/70 to-ink/85 p-10 text-center shadow-glow sm:p-16">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-[300px] w-[600px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-titan-600/20 blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-faint [background-size:48px_48px] opacity-30 [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_60%_at_50%_50%,#000,transparent_75%)]"></div>
      </div>

      <img src="/assets/logo-white.png" alt="Korvex" class="mx-auto h-8 w-auto opacity-90" />

      <h2 class="h-display mx-auto mt-7 max-w-3xl text-4xl leading-[1.02] sm:text-[3.2rem]">
        A Korvex não é pra todo mundo.
        <span class="block font-editorial italic font-normal text-titan-gradient">É pra quem decidiu não dividir o lucro com plataforma nenhuma.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-chrome-300/75">
        Mande sua operação pra análise e receba a condição desenhada pro seu volume.
        Migração assistida, do começo ao fim — sem parar de vender um único dia.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <a href={REGISTER_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary magnetic !px-7 !py-3.5 text-[15px]">
          Começar agora
          <span class="h-4 w-4" set:html={icon('arrow')}></span>
        </a>
        <a href={WHATSAPP_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ghost !px-7 !py-3.5 text-[15px]">
          <span class="h-5 w-5" set:html={icon('headset')}></span>
          Falar com um especialista
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-[13px] text-chrome-300/50">
        +400 players ativos • +R$129 milhões transacionados • Saque D0 no Pix
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
